{"type": "article", "id": 15446, "title": "无影灯", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 6617, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230622CiKQcEITn8X4Bg0V.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.134375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.cn/%E6%97%A0%E5%BD%B1%E7%81%AF-%E6%B8%A1%E8%BE%B9%E6%B7%B3%E4%B8%80/dp/B00O0QGPR2/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1443100499&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=%E6%97%A0%E5%BD%B1%E7%81%AF\" target=\"_blank\">《无影灯》</a>，渡边淳一\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>渡边纯一的小说，它讲述了一个与医生有关的故事。三十年间，这本小说重版近七十次，改编的电视剧曾高居收视率榜首，被日本媒体评为“最令人意犹未尽的作品”。刘同介绍，“一开始读的时候特别无聊，后来发现无聊也有无聊的好处，关于生与死的阐述还挺让人觉得是那么回事的。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}